{"tid":1672531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰之歌 - - -《收割者》","createTime":"2019-10-24T07:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T07:34:45.000Z","uid":53377,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0599feda4474055633046811a7b8c48d02b66b3d","tid":1672531,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2cWraqD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2cWraqD.jpg&h=36b8ae2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Els Segadors</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nCatalunya triomfant,<br />\ntornar&agrave; a ser rica i plena.<br />\nEndarrera aquesta gent<br />\ntan ufana i tan superba.<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>Tornada:</strong><br />\nBon cop de fal&ccedil;!<br />\nBon cop de fal&ccedil;, defensors de la terra!<br />\nBon cop de fal&ccedil;!</em><br />\n<br />\nAra &eacute;s hora, segadors.<br />\nAra &eacute;s hora d'estar alerta.<br />\nPer quan vingui un altre juny,<br />\nesmolem ben b&eacute; les eines.<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>Tornada</strong></em><br />\n<br />\nQue tremoli l'enemic,<br />\nen veient la nostra ensenya.<br />\nCom fem caure espigues d'or,<br />\nquan conv&eacute; seguem cadenes.<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>Tornada</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Zc-t_Z6EkaU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZc-t_Z6EkaU&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUobXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=f1aa377c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Zc-t_Z6EkaU</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n歌詞中文翻譯<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《收割者》</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n凱旋的加泰羅尼亞<br />\n要回復往日的富庶和美麗！<br />\n我們要把那些自負<br />\n而又卑鄙的人趕出去！<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>副歌</strong><br />\n手起鐮刀落！<br />\n手起鐮刀落！<br />\n保衛這片土地的人啊！<br />\n手起鐮刀落！</em><br />\n<br />\n收割者們啊，現在就是時候，<br />\n打醒十二分精神的時候。<br />\n我們要在下一個六月之前<br />\n把工具都磨鋒利！<br />\n<br />\n<em>副歌</em><br />\n<br />\n每當看見我們的旗幟<br />\n敵人們都會顫抖！<br />\n收割金色稻穗之日<br />\n就是斬斷鎖鏈之時！<br />\n<br />\n<em>副歌</em><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Els_Segadors#/languages\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FEls_Segadors%23%2Flanguages&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUobXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=0cceb6a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Els_Segadors#/languages</a>"},{"pid":"95f827400bb7fa0bcb61e0c8f46fc6d156e33588","tid":1672531,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R42FeTX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR42FeTX.jpg&h=0c47705b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚7-9 遮打花園<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad82e489738b2644fe47951a8db76e7161d3e73","tid":1672531,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"125d2f716052cc335929d918c8dbf48b1030cec9","tid":1672531,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"a9ba017edd3763a77e4292ee21b62735b664cbdc","tid":1672531,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:16:39.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"8276ece2050087f21a9c0ce58a6d24ee58112f25","tid":1672531,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:18:10.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"2241811371b4371f4c633c20ed4570ebd850e39b","tid":1672531,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:19:30.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"778f6d4b01d0889a6c91c31a9398d1f6889321d6","tid":1672531,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:20:50.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"671618863a542a1ddd98c4b8d4181d570bbb57cb","tid":1672531,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:21:09.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"14d46f49f513df13f217d5aedce90df3681018e0","tid":1672531,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:21:29.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"c1b406872b333e4104c3285cd6230deb31acee2e","tid":1672531,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:21:46.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"ccf6402e861b6277a0b5f94d87a11b46fa7ee0fa","tid":1672531,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"4769a0e0f606a4fc85c85b73c75003b121b01252","tid":1672531,"uid":27225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:33:53.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"8c0a5c2d5b152109dce80d8be2a5e6683d18eb3c","tid":1672531,"uid":27225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:34:05.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"6a6372be299bfa542e8d8a36f01dfc3bc7ddf2b7","tid":1672531,"uid":27225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:34:15.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"b4ebe2940697fe6dbd36e8486ef00141126b563b","tid":1672531,"uid":27225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:34:29.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"b4860fca02eb3d3cb756d5138f1410838b0f47d8","tid":1672531,"uid":27225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:34:45.000Z","msg":"拉"}]}